snippet.title: Greyhill Incident - Console Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist it Now on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1905020/Greyhill_Incident/

This story-driven Survival-Horror game about an classic Alien-Invasion takes place during the early 90s. As Ryan Baker, equipped with a baseball bat and a few bullets in his revolver, the story takes you across the atmospheric neighborhood of Greyhill which is invaded by UFOs & Grey Aliens.
